  "title": "Campanion",
  "description": "A camping mod adding all kind of utilities related to the outdoors.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SoDcupL.png\" alt=\"campanion_banner\" width=\"1200\" height=\"450\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Campainion is a camping companion that adds items and utilities to improve your life away from home.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"149\" height=\"50\" /></strong></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Campanion requires <a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/use/\">Fabric Loader</a> and <a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\">Fabric API</a></strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Check out the <a href=\"https://discord.gg/jEGF5fb\">Terraformers Discord Server</a> to chat about Campanion and other Fabric mods!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Visit the <a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki\">Campanion Wiki</a> to learn more about all the features</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>About Campanion:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Campanion is a drop in and play solution to the nomadic lifestyle for Minecraft 1.15.2 and above running on the Fabric Mod loader. It was originally created as a ModFest 1.15 entry in April of 2020, but we enjoyed the project so much, that we plan to continue to support and update it in the future as new versions release, and as we come up with new ideas. The mod adds various decoration and utility items that are guaranteed to liven up your Minecraft world.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The goal of Campanion was to create a themed mod that adds all kinds of features that we wanted in the game or otherwise be believe should be in the game anyways.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Features:</strong></span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Rope-Bridges\">Rope Bridges</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Rope-Ladders\">Rope Ladders</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Grappling-Hook\">Grappling Hooks</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Backpacks\">Backpacks</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Tents\">Tents</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Sleeping-Bags\">Sleeping Bags</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Spears\">Spears<br /></a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Lawn-Chairs\">Lawn Chairs</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Smores\">S'mores</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Skipping-Stones\">Skipping Stones</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Leather-Tanning\">Leather Tanning</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Howling-Wolves\">Howling Wolves</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/TerraformersMC/Campanion/wiki/Materials\">Materials</a></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Flares</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Colorable Fires</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Other Mods by Terraformers:</strong></span></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Check out the sister biome mods, <a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/traverse\">Traverse </a>and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/terrestria\">Terrestria</a>:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/traverse\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZvKFrFt.png\" width=\"267\" height=\"100\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/terrestria\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s2ubJa1.png\" width=\"267\" height=\"100\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Terrestria and Traverse work well with Campanion and provides many new locations for you to camp at..&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Check out the Terraformers Nether biome expansion, <a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/cinderscapes\">Cinderscapes</a>:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/cinderscapes\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h7223x7.png\" width=\"267\" height=\"100\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Who ever said you couldn't camp in the nether? Cinderscapes adds many new beautiful yet frightening landscapes that you can camp in (just make sure not to use a sleeping bag in the nether!).</p>",
